VideoGames.GameDescription: Elden Ring is a 2022 action role-playing game developed by FromSoftware and published by Bandai Namco Entertainment. It was directed by Hidetaka Miyazaki with worldbuilding provided by fantasy writer George R. R. Martin.

Old Rag Mountain Loop is a 9.5 mile heavily trafficked loop trail located near Etlan, Virginia that features a river and is rated as difficult. The trail is primarily used for hiking and is best used from May until October.
